Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.60,0:03:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.17,0:03:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}天神
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.82,0:03:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}既然我已经活不久了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.62,0:03:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}如果我的牺牲能拯救大家
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.11,0:03:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我不害怕 我不害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.77,0:03:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}这家伙太强了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.62,0:03:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}风
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.89,0:03:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}夏凛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.26,0:04:00.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}你们快去找友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.57,0:04:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我来挡住它
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.68,0:04:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}你一个人挡住？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.18,0:04:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}别小看我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.46,0:04:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我还有满开在
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.39,0:04:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}夏凛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.88,0:04:19.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}得向友奈道歉 带她一起回去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.75,0:04:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}东西无双 三好夏凛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.07,0:04:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}敬请看好我此生最大的疯狂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.49,0:04:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}这样下去…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.56,0:04:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}姐姐 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.87,0:04:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}树 这里能交给你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.99,0:04:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}嗯 姐姐去找友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.09,0:04:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}嗯 我去把友奈带回来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.99,0:05:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}你可别出事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.00,0:05:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}风学姐 上来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.19,0:05:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}东乡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.78,0:05:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}那就去友奈那边吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.41,0:05:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我会开到最大战速
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.41,0:05:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}防护罩被…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.04,0:05:26.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}都是这家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.47,0:05:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}开什么玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.34,0:05:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}浑蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.04,0:05:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}园子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.66,0:05:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}不可以一个人冲太前面哦 小鱼干
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.40,0:05:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}树
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.68,0:05:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}一起保护好 友奈要回来的这片家园吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.83,0:06:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}东乡 看那里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.26,0:06:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}那边是神树大人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.65,0:06:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}友奈就在前面
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.19,0:06:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.59,0:06:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}没完没了的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.16,0:06:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}风学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.87,0:06:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}全员弃舰
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.78,0:06:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}东乡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.38,0:06:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}神树大人在阻止我们
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.63,0:06:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}才不管呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.82,0:06:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}就算是神树大人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.04,0:07:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我这次也不会退让
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.45,0:07:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}路被…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.97,0:07:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.16,0:08:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}东乡 做得到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.37,0:08:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}必须的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.29,0:08:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}那么我来给你…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.93,0:08:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}开路！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.47,0:08:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}这里是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.56,0:08:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.48,0:08:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我能靠精灵之力回去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.07,0:09:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.90,0:09:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}东乡 为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.60,0:09:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我们回去吧 我是来接你的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.77,0:09:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}你宁可这么做 也不肯把她交给我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.29,0:09:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}友奈 我这就救你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.93,0:09:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}但是如果我不牺牲 世界就会灭亡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.14,0:09:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}既然必须有人牺牲 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.29,0:09:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}不需要你…不需要任何人牺牲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.37,0:09:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我不想再有好朋友被抢走了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.17,0:10:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我只要忍耐就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.10,0:10:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.45,0:10:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}说真心话吧 害怕就告诉我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.20,0:10:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}都告诉我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.33,0:10:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我们既然是朋友 就向我求救啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.79,0:10:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我不想啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.48,0:10:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我很怕
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.09,0:10:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我不能说 但我…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.87,0:10:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}也不想死啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.35,0:10:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}不想跟大家分开啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.31,0:10:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.36,0:10:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我们一直很拼命的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.34,0:10:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}为什么还要这样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.96,0:10:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.22,0:10:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}好想 好想…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.67,0:10:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}永远和大家在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.34,0:11:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}友奈 手伸出来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.34,0:11:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}东乡 救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.94,0:11:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.51,0:11:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}东乡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.10,0:11:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}怎么会…为什么非要阻止我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.42,0:11:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}东乡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.18,0:11:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.99,0:11:32.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.10,0:11:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}东乡…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.63,0:11:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}不要
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.22,0:11:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}不对
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.01,0:12:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我们不想这样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.23,0:12:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我感谢神树大人 但是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.94,0:12:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}但是 已经够了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.04,0:12:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}如果要得到新世界就得牺牲别人 牺牲朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.71,0:12:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我不要这种新世界
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.17,0:12:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}这就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.96,0:13:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}神树大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.47,0:13:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}每个人都不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.27,0:13:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}如果你真的想拯救人类
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.57,0:13:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}能不能
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.54,0:13:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}再相信一次人类呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.02,0:14:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.90,0:14:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}会继续过人类的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.88,0:14:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.60,0:14:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}东乡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.07,0:14:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.07,0:14:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}东乡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.00,0:14:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}东乡！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.21,0:14:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}对不起 对不起 都是我说太过分了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.98,0:14:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我 我才要道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.47,0:14:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}对你做了好过分的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.21,0:15:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}没关系 已经没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.12,0:15:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}怎么办 世界要毁灭了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.65,0:15:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}这不是你的错
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.20,0:15:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}如果世界真的要毁灭
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.53,0:15:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我们也无能为力了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.66,0:15:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}牛鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.64,0:15:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}你要干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.06,0:15:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}不要紧的 好温暖啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.11,0:16:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.11,0:16:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我们会作为人类去战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.60,0:16:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我们想活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.11,0:16:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}勇者不屈 在哪里跌倒就在哪里站起来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.58,0:16:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}上啊 友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.61,0:16:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}为了友奈的幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.00,0:16:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}有志者
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.77,0:17:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}事竟成
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.44,0:17:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}勇者部 Fight
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.13,0:17:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}勇者就靠毅力！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.16,0:17:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}勇者之拳！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.39,0:18:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}火焰…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.77,0:18:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}这…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.79,0:18:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}和以前不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.51,0:19:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}牛鬼…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.60,0:19:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.05,0:19:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}再见
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.27,0:19:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.72,0:19:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}世界
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.74,0:19:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}还在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.31,0:19:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}神树大人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.83,0:19:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.40,0:19:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}散花了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.40,0:20:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}还是平时的蓝天
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.37,0:20:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}怎么了友奈 身体不舒服吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.79,0:20:17.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}没有了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.57,0:20:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}烙印消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.56,0:20:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}大家
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.65,0:20:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}大家 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.94,0:20:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我才是 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.33,0:20:38.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}夏凛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.93,0:20:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}欢迎回来 友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.27,0:20:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.87,0:21:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}于内陆山区至市区一带发生的大规模火灾
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.29,0:21:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}受灾面积一周内扩大至约一万公顷
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.69,0:21:08.52,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}由于长期避难 居民们倍感疲惫
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.52,0:21:11.29,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}要求大赦针对接下来的事 拿出合理方针
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.15,0:21:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}也就是说 大赦早知道墙外的情况了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.45,0:21:16.00,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}请看 本土已经化为了毫无生气的废墟
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.35,0:21:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}人们今后只能靠着有限的资源生存下去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.00,0:21:20.26,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}涌出的石油据说是神树大人的残骸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.84,0:21:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}孩子们是无辜的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.47,0:21:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}地之神消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.59,0:21:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}失去庇护的人类 只能靠有限的资源活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.55,0:21:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}一定会发生混乱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.21,0:21:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}但这样就好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.25,0:21:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我为她们的选择感到骄傲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.93,0:21:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}新时代应当是孩子们的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.02,0:21:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}大人要为孩子负起责任
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.76,0:21:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}这是我们的天命
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.05,0:22:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}勇者部变回了勇者部
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.27,0:22:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}风学姐考上了高中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.77,0:22:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}下一任部长竟然是树
